page.title: 02FASHION IN FULHAM
page.content:
There are many types of fashion in 1985.Different types of people wear different clothes. The' posers' wear expensive makes of clothes like Tacchini,Fila & Kappa,sports wear.'Punks,Rockabillys and Hippies shop up the Kings Road. Sometimes they even come from other countries to go there.Rockabillys wear baggy trousers and have flat hair styles.Hippys wear heavy metal clothes like old and worn out jean jackets. Punks have weird hairstyles full of colour and also wear wierd clothes. Young people today like wearing long baggy shirts and trousers.
Girls wear patan shoes,boys trainers with makes like Adidas,Nike,Puma & New Balance.These can cost up to 100 pounds.
